<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Mind should be all about Mind Control, as that is what the Sorcerer is known for.<BR>That being said, i believe the following are changes that should be made from what the game is currently at (2/26/02):<P>-Our Amnesia should interrupt and have a person lose their target.<P>-Confusion should be fixed.  It is now currently not even usable in PvE, and as we all know has no use in RvR.<P>-Str/Con Debuff needs to have a place in RvR to even be cast.  Increase the range so that it is worth being cast.  Right now if i'm at range 1500, i'm gonna either DD, Root, or Mezz, not Debuff.<P>-As the main mind/crowd control class in albion, we are the only main in this area without stun.  However, I dont even want stun.  Just remove magical based stuns from the game.  Have stun only be administered through Melee (Shield or Weapon Hits).<P>-Need more Charmable Mobs, and more variety with the mobs.  I'd like to see more mobs that are weaker melee but buff me, or that are casters so they have some type of AoE DD or AoE DoT, etc...  I'd like variety so that you can choose which type of pet to have for whichever battle.<P>--------------------<P>Cavalier<BR>Hand of God Sorcerer - Palomides Server.<BR>Carrying around a worthless Melee Proc Staff
</FONT>
