<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
What Cavalier said.<P>I'd like to add:<P><BR>CHARMING:<BR>-------------<P>-Cleric pets not healing/buffing efficiently, Caster pets just going into meele instead of casting spells.<P>-Clerics/Friars don't see how many hit points they have healed your pet for. Also be nice to see how much your pet is hitting for and being hit for.<P>-Pet buffs don't show up correctly in the pet window.<P>-Pets warping around.<P>-Need more control over pets. Decide if you want them to use meele or arrows, make them able to sprint after a target, etc.<P><BR>MEZ:<BR>-------------<BR> <BR>-Mezzing gets the Sorcerer killed way too much. It would be nice if a mob that breaks mez would randomly pick a target in your group instead of going for the Sorcerer.<P>-Make mez give realm points for RvR.<P>-Charming a mob breaks mez on linked mobs.<P>-Mobs go in and out of war mode while mezed, making it difficult to charm them.<P>-Mez remains on mob after its been charmed.<P>-Cannot mez over a Minstrles mez. "already has that effect" even after the mez has been broken.<P>-When mez is broken on a mob, the mob will complete its last action before it was mezed.<P><BR>DEBUFFS:<BR>-------------<P>-Debuffs are useless, make them do something.<P>-Make debuffs give realm points for RvR.<P><BR>SPEED BUFF:<BR>-------------<P>-If you're grouped with a Minstrel and you go out of range of his speed song it takes 6 seconds for your speed buff to start working again.<P>EDIT: Something I'd like to see that would never happen, move all our debuffs to the body line, then move our Mind Blast spell to the mind line.<P>--------------------<P>Garen, Paper Minstrel<BR>Albion, Percival
